            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="2017.342" end="x">Ja.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Adolph Heisler</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#heislerA" start="2018.527" end="x">Die hat man getötet und verbrannt.</span>
