        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="2362.741" end="x">Nach der Befreiung haben Sie Fleck-Typhus bekommen?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Adolph Heisler</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#heislerA" start="2364.532" end="x">Ja. </span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="2364.998" end="x">Ja. </span>
        </li>
